OL,3,CSurgeons use mixed reality goggles to
OL,4,C'see inside' body for first time in UK
OL,6,FScottish surgeons have performed an
OL,7,Foperation using technology which
OL,8,Fallows them to "see inside" a
OL,9,Fpatient's body.
OL,11,FThe Institute for Neurological
OL,12,FSciences in Glasgow used mixed reality
OL,13,F(MR) technology during an operation on
OL,14,F75-year-old Carol Toal.
OL,16,FThe procedure involved a system called
OL,17,FSpine Mixed Reality Navigation, which
OL,18,Ffuses X-rays with external images of a
OL,19,Fpatient.
