OL,3,CSurgeons use mixed reality goggles to
OL,4,C'see inside' body for first time in UK
OL,6,FIt involves images which are relayed
OL,7,Fthrough MR goggles rather than on a
OL,8,Fscreen.
OL,10,FThe goggles also provide an accurate
OL,11,Fview of the body and spinal anatomy.
OL,13,FMs Toal received the operation to
OL,14,Fcorrect a spinal misalignment, treat a
OL,15,Fspinal cyst and decompress spinal
OL,16,Fnerves.
OL,18,FThe issues left Mrs Toal, from Irvine,
OL,19,FScotland, with chronic pain in her leg
OL,20,Fand back.
