OL,3,CSurgeons use mixed reality goggles to
OL,4,C'see inside' body for first time in UK
OL,6,FShe described the operation as
OL,7,F"lifesaving" and less than a week
OL,8,Flater, she no longer suffered from
OL,9,Fchronic pain.
OL,11,FMohamed Abdelsadg, consultant
OL,12,Fneurosurgeon and complex spine
OL,13,Fsurgeon, said: "The result is we are
OL,14,Feffectively able to see inside a
OL,15,Fpatient's body while we are performing
OL,16,Fthe operation.
OL,18,F"This means the surgery is much more
OL,19,Faccurate, is much less invasive, and
OL,20,Fminimises surgical damage to other
OL,21,Ftissue."
