OL,3,CSurgeons use mixed reality goggles to
OL,4,C'see inside' body for first time in UK
OL,6,F"We already do a lot of minimally
OL,7,Finvasive work using an earlier
OL,8,FBrainlab system, so we were familiar
OL,9,Fwith the set-up and this felt more
OL,10,Flike a software upgrade rather than a
OL,11,Fcompletely new system," Mr Abdelsadg
OL,12,Fadded.
OL,14,F"Also, the spinal neurosurgeons
OL,15,Farranged for three days' training in
OL,16,Fthe Institute's Teasdale simulation
OL,17,Fsuite, which allowed us to familiarise
OL,18,Fourselves with the kit. This meant the
OL,19,Ftechnical part of the operation went
OL,20,Fwell.
