OL,6,F"Our early experience was certainly
OL,7,Fpositive and we all feel this system
OL,8,Fhas real potential to build on the
OL,9,Fadvanced neurosurgical work we do at
OL,10,Fthe institute."
OL,12,FThe institute is the third-only centre
OL,13,Fworldwide to have used the technology.
OL,15,FIt also provides specialised care for
OL,16,Fpatients, and is operated by NHS
OL,17,FGreater Glasgow and Clyde (NHSGGC),
OL,18,Fwhich welcomed "innovations".
